  "title": "12 Months Contract Credit Admin Officer (Foreign Bank) #BJT",
  "description": "<p><strong>Job Description:</strong></p>\n<p><br></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Ensure the approved terms of the credit proposals are accurately reflected</li>\n  <li>Liaise with lawyers and RMs for mortgage redemption matters</li>\n  <li>Check duly executed security documentation / conditions and ensure they are in order before limit input</li>\n  <li>Maintain custody of credit files for dept</li>\n  <li>Follow up with RMs on outstanding documentation</li>\n</ul>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><strong>Application Procedures</strong></p>\n<p>Interested candidates, please email your resume to:</p>\n<p>Attention: Jamie Tan Pei Zhen (CEI No. R2199473)</p>\n<p><strong>jamietan@recruitexpress.com.sg</strong></p>\n<p>Recruit Express Pte Ltd (EA No. 99C4599)</p>",
